<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<script type="text/javascript"><% include "h_serverType.html" %></script>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head><meta http-equiv="Content-Script-Type" content="text/javascript" />
  <link href="/css/popup.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <link href="/css/custom.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <link href="/css/icons.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />

  <title>iDRAC7: Storage Summary</title>
  <script src="/js/prototype.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/Clarity.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="h_common.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	</head>
<body onload="javascript:popUp.initialize(true);">

  <div class="popup_container">
    <script type="text/javascript">writeHelpHeader(<%=dracType %>); </script>
    <div class="popup_content">
      <div class="popup_content_top_right">
        <div class="popup_content_top_left">
          <div class="popup_content_top">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="popup_content_right">
        <div class="popup_content_left">
          <div class="popup_content_middle">
            <div class="popup_page_title">
              				<span id="helpTitle"> Storage Overview</span>
               <div class="popup_line">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="popup-jump-bar">
              <span class="popup-jump-items">Jump to:
                <a id="cc3" href="#Alerts" class="popup-jump-bar">Recently Logged Storage Events</a>
                |<a id="A14" href="#Other" class="popup-jump-bar">Other Options</a>
              </span>
              <div class="popup_jumpbar-line">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="popup_overflow">
              <a name="top"></a>
              <div class="popup_inner_content">
                <div>
                  <p>Use this page to view the summary of the storage components and 
					the recently logged events. This page is refreshed 
					automatically every 30 seconds.</p>
					</div>
              <div class="popup_subheader">                
                <span id="Storage_summary"> Storage Summary </span> 
                <div class="popup_subheaderline">
                </div>
                </div>
               <div class="popup_inner_content">
              	<p>This section provides a pie-chart view of the physical disks 
				in the storage sub-system, grouped based on their states. 
				Also, provides a summary of the disks available in the system:</p>
					<ul>
									<li>Physical disks</li>
									<li>Virtual disks</li>
									<li>Global hot spares</li>
									<li>Dedicated hot spares</li>
					</ul>
					<p>&nbsp;Click the <b>Physical Disks</b> or <b>Virtual Disks</b> link to 
					view the respective pages.</p>
				</div>
              
              <div class="popup_subheader">
                <a name="Alerts"></a>
                <div class="popup_backtotop">
                  <a href="javascript:popUp.scrolltoTop()">Back to top</a>
                </div>
                <span id="Alerts"> Recently Logged Storage Events</span>
                <div class="popup_subheaderline">
                </div>
              </div>
			  <div class="popup_inner_content">
			  <div>
					<p>This section lists the latest 10 storage events.</p>
					</div>
                                            
                                                <div class="popup_infolist">
                                                    <table>
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="item">
                                                               <span><b>Severity</b></span>
                                                            </td>
                                                            <td class="desc">
                                                                <p>
                                                                    Displays the 
																	severity 
																	level for 
																	the event:</p>
																<ul>
                                      <li><span class="status_ok"> &#8212;</span> Informational<br></br></li>
                                      <li><span class="status_noncritical"> &#8212; </span> Warning<br></br></li>
                                      <li><span class="status_critical">&#8212; </span>Critical<br></br></li>
                                      <li><span class="status_unknown">&#8212; </span>Information Not Available</li>                                                                        
                                    </ul>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="item">
                                                                <span><b>Date/Time</b></span>
                                                            </td>
                                                            <td class="desc">
                                                                Displays the 
																date and time 
																when the event 
																has occurred.
																</td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td class="item">
                                                                <span><b>Description</b></span>
                                                            </td>
                                                            <td class="desc">
                                                                <p>
                                                                    Provides a 
																	brief 
																	description 
																	of the 
																	event.</p>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    </table>
                                              
                                            </div>
                
              </div>
            
              <script type="text/javascript">
                writeHelpOtherBegin();
				writeHelpOtherEnd();
			  </script>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
	</div>
  </div>
	</body>
</html>
